[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmpldemodr_[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report from a libFuzzer run on the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness reveals a one-byte stack buffer overflow in the Little CMS [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlcms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m library. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe overflow is detected in the function `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalled during a device-link color transformation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue surfaces when processing a fuzzer-generated input via the fuzzer harness; the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness itself merely triggers the code path and is not the root cause.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue Detail  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  During a fuzzing session [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`-[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m of the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbinary, AddressSanitizer reports a “stack-buffer-overflow” while executing [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` in `cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130:13[0m[39m`. The read of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m occurs [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m bytes after[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe start of a stack variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m allocated in the stack frame of [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The report indicates a stack-buffer-overflow vulnerability. A one-byte read goes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpast the boundary of a stack-allocated object, violating memory safety.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key Observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The overflow is triggered by `UnrollChunkyBytes`, which is invoked indirectly [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` and `cmsDoTransform` [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – `CachedXFORM` [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The failing stack frame [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m allocates multiple local [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobjects [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`, `dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with `i.i` sized [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes; the overflow access touches offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m, just beyond that object’s bounds.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • AddressSanitizer’s shadow-memory dump confirms the overflow falls into a right [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mredzone, demonstrating a true out-of-bounds access on the stack.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` in `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimply feeds raw input to the transformation pipeline; no instrumentation in the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness contributes to the overflow.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code Areas for Investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  To understand the full impact and root cause, the following components should be [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreviewed:  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. cmspack.c, function `UnrollChunkyBytes`: buffer allocations and index [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputations around line [0m[1;36m130[0m[39m.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. cmsvirt.c, function `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`: how local buffers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare allocated and populated.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. cmsxform.c, functions `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, `cmsDoTransform`, and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CachedXFORM`: data flow leading to `UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Any related packing or chunk-handling utilities that feed into [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`, to assess bounds checking.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ [0m[33mFUZZER[0m[39m=[0m[35mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer[0m                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m36[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1.5[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m52[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses limited precision to floor[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:    union [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mv > [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v = [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:        wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mindex[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:        accum += Stride;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInit + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m147[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtra == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && SwapFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m148[0m[39m:        cmsUInt16Number tmp = wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m150[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mmemmove[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, &wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnChan-[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:        wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan-[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = tmp;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m152[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m153[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:    return accum;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsUNUSED_PARAMETER[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsUNUSED_PARAMETER[0m[1;39m([0m[39mStride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:113[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m124[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPremul && Extra[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:            alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:        accum += Extra;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:    else[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPremul && Extra[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:            alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:143[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m145[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!ExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:        accum += Extra;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m145[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The function `UnrollChunkyBytes` in `src/cmspack.c` unpacks pixel channels [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m“chunky” layout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but ignores the provided `Stride` parameter when skipping “extra”[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchannels before and after the core channels.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - As a result, with `Extra == [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` and `Stride > [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`, the pointer arithmetic `accum[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+= Extra;` advances only by one byte rather than one entire pixel plane [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Extra * Stride` bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This leads to a one-byte under-skip and thus a one-byte [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout-of-bounds read/writes on the scratch buffer on the stack, as detected by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Additionally, the premultiplication branch in the “else” path reads [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` instead of `accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan * Stride[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, also ignoring `Stride` and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrisking misaligned reads.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High-Level Fix  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Incorporate `Stride` into all pointer‐skipping logic** in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`, mirroring the approach used in `UnrollPlanarBytes`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Replace** each `accum += Extra;` with `accum += Extra * Stride;`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Adjust** the premultiplication read in the non-`ExtraFirst` branch from [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` to `accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan * Stride[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Open `src/cmspack.c` and locate `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m95[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In the `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Change  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        accum += Extra;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        to  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        accum += Extra * Stride;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In the `else` branch, change the premul read from:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      to  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan * Stride[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Later, in the `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!ExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Change  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        accum += Extra;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        to  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        accum += Extra * Stride;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Leave the final `return accum;` and any existing swap-first logic unchanged. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Rebuild and run the existing test suite plus the fuzzer harness to confirm [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe overflow is resolved and no regressions occur.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Correctness**: By applying `Extra * Stride`, the code now advances the input[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer by the full width of the “extra” channels [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., one channel plane[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing the one-byte under-skip that triggered the overflow.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Symmetry**: This change makes the chunky-unpack logic parallel to the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready-validated planar variant [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollPlanarBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which uses `accum += Extra [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m* Stride;`.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Minimal impact**: No other functionality is altered; performance impact is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnegligible [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly two extra integer multiplications per pixel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Preserves existing behavior**: When `Extra == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, `Extra * Stride == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, so [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe skip logic is a no-op as before. All other branches and post-processing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mswap-first, premul scaling[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain intact.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **No external or harness modifications**: The fix lives entirely within the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary’s unpack routine, aligning with the requirement to avoid touching harness, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests, or external dependencies.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ***Performance***: A trivial extra multiply is added; this is unlikely to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maffect real-world throughput.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ***Testing***: Ensure that all image transforms [0m[1;39m([0m[39mespecially those involving [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“extra” alpha or named color axes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m still produce correct output. Add a unit test [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith a simple chunky profile that has an extra channel and a known stride > [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcatch any misalignment.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ***Regression***: Run full regression [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding color-profiling tests[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirm no unintended effects.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>src/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:113[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m124[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>src/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:143[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m145[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m during a fuzzing run of cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer. The overflow [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs while processing a chunky pixel buffer and propagates through CachedXFORM, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsDoTransform and cmsTransform2DeviceLink. A patch was attempted in src/cmspack.c [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto multiply pointer increments by the sample stride [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchanging `accum += Extra;` to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`accum += Extra * Stride;` and adjusting an alpha index similarly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. After [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, the same one-byte read overflow at the same [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress and code location reappeared, indicating the patch did not resolve the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer invocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggered AddressSanitizer reporting a stack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c line [0m[1;36m130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow read is a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read just past a stack variable boundary [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset [0m[1;36m36[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the frame of cmsTransform2DeviceLink[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash stack trace flows through: UnrollChunkyBytes → CachedXFORM → [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsDoTransform → CreateNamedColorDevicelink → cmsTransform2DeviceLink → [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLLVMFuzzerTestOneInput.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan indicates the overflow accesses just past the end of the local array `i.i` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min cmsTransform2DeviceLink’s stack frame.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Changes were applied in src/cmspack.c around the loops in UnrollChunkyBytes:  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * In the first branch, `accum += Extra;` was replaced with `accum += Extra * [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStride;`.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * In the same branch, the alpha channel index was updated from `accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan * Stride[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * In the final section, `accum += Extra;` was likewise changed to `accum += Extra[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m* Stride;`.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The modified cmspack.c still compiled and integrated into the library; the fuzzer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwas rebuilt and run under the same conditions.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPost-patch result  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- AddressSanitizer again detected the identical stack-buffer-overflow at [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m during UnrollChunkyBytes.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The error report and stack trace remain unchanged, pointing to the same boundary [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mviolation and the same local variables in cmsTransform2DeviceLink.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The pointer arithmetic and buffer length calculations in UnrollChunkyBytes [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m relative to the sample stride and number of channels.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The layout and allocation of the local arrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, to determine expected input buffer size versus[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual access pattern.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:96[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m104[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m96:c[0m[39mmsUInt8Number* [0m[1;35mUnrollChunkyBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCMSREGISTER _cmsTRANSFORM* info,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* accum,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt32Number Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number nChan      = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number DoSwap     = [0m[1;35mT_DOSWAP[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number Reverse    = [0m[1;35mT_FLAVOR[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number SwapFirst  = [0m[1;35mT_SWAPFIRST[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:113[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m124[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPremul && Extra[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:            alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:        accum += Extra;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:    else[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPremul && Extra[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:            alpha_factor = [0m[1;35m_cmsToFixedDomain[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1104[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The stack-buffer-overflow does *not* originate in cmspack.c itself but in how [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwe call `cmsDoTransform` from `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We set the *input format* to `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` but then pass the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress of a [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit loop counter [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`&i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as the “chunky-byte” input buffer.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Internally, `UnrollChunkyBytes` assumes the input pointer references `nChan` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchannels × `BytesPerChannel` bytes. Supplying only [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsUInt32Number`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcauses reads past that boundary, hence the ASan overflow at `accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Logic  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must continue using `[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, …, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the loop, invoking the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame transform pipeline.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must not change any fuzzing harness, test code, or external library.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must continue to set the formatter via `[0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Plan  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `src/cmsvirt.c`, inside `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, replace the in-loop [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall that currently does:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   with code that:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Declares a *[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit* variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmatching the `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` setting[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m on the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack for each iteration.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Initializes it with the loop index: `idx16 = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi;`  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Passes `&idx16` to `cmsDoTransform`.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Concretely:  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         cmsUInt16Number idx16 = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &idx16, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures that the input buffer is at least [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand—since [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` semantically has one channel— satisfies the expectations [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof `UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, eliminating any over-read.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By matching the declared `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and using a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit buffer, we no longer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhand `UnrollChunkyBytes` an undersized pointer.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This preserves the entire transform pipeline [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding `CachedXFORM`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform`, `UnrollChunkyBytes`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without altering its assumptions.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness, test, or utility code is modified; tests and fuzz targets continue[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto operate unchanged.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - *Side Effect:* Slight per-iteration stack usage increase [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes instead of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreusing the `&i` pointer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - *Mitigation:* Negligible; the overhead is constant and minimal.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - *Validation:* Rebuild the library and rerun the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m+ runs under ASan to confirm the absence of the previous [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mASan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m stack-buffer-overflow in the Little CMS library. The overflow occurs in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when called via cmsDoTransform → [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink in `cmsvirt.c`. A patch was attempted: changing the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex variable from a plain `int i` to a `cmsUInt16Number idx16`, and passing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`&idx16` to `cmsDoTransform` instead of `&i`. After applying this patch, the same [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mASan error reoccurred, now reporting an overflow of the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte `idx16` variable at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read just past its boundary. The overflow remains in the same code paths.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Running the fuzzer for the virtual profile code in Little CMS [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with AddressSanitizer enabled produces:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • A stack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130:13[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • ASan reports a single-byte read beyond the top of a stack buffer.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • In the frame for `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, a local variable named `i.i` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccupies bytes [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and the overflow occurs at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read, indicating code in UnrollChunkyBytes is indexing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone byte past a buffer allocated on the stack.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The local `int i` in the calling function is passed by address to [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform`; ASan attributes the overflow back to that local.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The issue consistently reproduces in the same code path, suggesting that the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnrollChunkyBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is interpreting its inputs in a way that can [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceed the bounds of the provided buffer.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `src/cmsvirt.c`, within the loop that applies the transform to each named [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcolor:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Original code:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Patched code:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt16Number idx16 = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi;[0m                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The intention was to use a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit stack variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`idx16`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of the [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`i`.[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, ASan still reports:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • A stack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes at the same source line.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • In the patched frame, `idx16.i` occupies bytes [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m34[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; the overflow read [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs at offset [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m, one byte past the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte variable.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The call chain and overall failure pattern remain unchanged.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of UnrollChunkyBytes in `cmspack.c`, specifically how it [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputes and accesses its stack buffers.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and expected size of the input buffer that UnrollChunkyBytes [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muses—whether it should accept inputs of arbitrary bit-depth or whether upstream [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode must enforce limits.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The invocation of `cmsDoTransform` and how frame arguments [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumber of samples, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbit-depth, input buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are marshaled by CachedXFORM.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The broader logic in CreateNamedColorDevicelink and cmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cmsvirt.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, including how local arrays `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, and `LUT` are declared[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand sized, and whether any assumptions about input dimensions are violated.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
