[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m274[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m275[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m276[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfOut, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m277[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m278[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < LineCount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m279[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m280[0m[39m:        accum = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39min + strideIn;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m281[0m[39m:        output = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mout + strideOut;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m282[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m283[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < PixelsPerLine; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m284[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m285[0m[39m:            accum = p->[0m[1;35mFromInputFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, fIn, accum, Stride->BytesPerPlaneIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m286[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m287[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Any gamut check to do?[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m288[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->GamutCheck != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m289[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m290[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Evaluate gamut marker.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m291[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineEvalFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn, &OutOfGamut, p->GamutCheck[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m292[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m293[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Is current color out of gamut?[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m294[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOutOfGamut > [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m295[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m296[0m[39m:                    _cmsAlarmCodesChunkType* ContextAlarmCodes = [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m_cmsAlarmCodesChunkType*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m_cmsContextGetClientChunk[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->ContextID, [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAlarmCodesContext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m297[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m298[0m[39m:                    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Certainly, out of gamut[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m299[0m[39m:                    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; c < cmsMAXCHANNELS; c++[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m300[0m[39m:                        fOut[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = ContextAlarmCodes->AlarmCodes[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m65535.[0m[39m0F;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1094[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1104[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1094[0m[39m:    nc2 ->ColorantCount = [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineOutputChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->Lut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1095[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1097[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1099[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Remove spurious line-number prefixes**  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The last patch attempt accidentally injected text like `[0m[1;36m1097[0m[39m:` into `cmsvirt.c`.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese tokens are not valid C syntax and must be removed entirely. Ensure the code [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround lines [0m[1;36m1094[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1104[0m[39m in `src/cmsvirt.c` is restored to proper C statements [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout numeric prefixes.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Correct the `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call**  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The root cause of the AddressSanitizer stack-buffer-overflow in [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` is that the input‐pixel format passed to [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat` lacks explicit byte‐ and channel‐count flags.  As a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresult, the transform pipeline falls back to the generic chunky‐bytes unpacker [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with an incorrect channel count, overrunning the fixed-size [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocal buffer in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   To fix this:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **OR** the `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` bitmask with the correct `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` flags so that the input formatter knows exactly “[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m bytes” [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e. the named‐color index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Leave the second parameter [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe output‐pixel format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m unchanged, since it [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly specifies `[0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnDeviceChannels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Concretely, replace the existing call:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   with:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mT_TYPE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` remains `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX`, selecting the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecialized named‐color unpacker.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` becomes `[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtypically [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer will read the full index.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` becomes [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, preventing any multi‐channel loop in the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munpacker.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Verify the loop is preserved**  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Keep the subsequent loop intact:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This loop drives the fuzzer only through the named‐color index path and is not [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto be altered.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Justification and side‐effect analysis**  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By explicitly encoding the byte and channel counts for the named‐color index [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput, we guarantee that the correct formatter [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot the generic chunky [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m‐bit [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munpacker[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is used.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This prevents `UnrollChunkyBytes` from running with a bogus `nChan` and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrunning its local buffer.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The output‐format code path is unchanged, so existing devicelink behavior and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests continue to work.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or fuzz-related code is modified; all tests and external APIs [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain untouched.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach aligns with other `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` invocations in Little[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCMS, which always OR together `TYPE_*`, `BYTES_SH`, and `CHANNELS_SH` bits for each[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mside of the transform.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Implementation steps**  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open `src/cmsvirt.c`.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Find the block around the `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CreateNamedColorDevicelink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginally lines ~[0m[1;36m1096[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1104[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Remove the numeric prefixes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;36m1097[0m[39m:`, `[0m[1;36m1098[0m[39m:`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and reformat the call as[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshown above.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Rebuild and re-run the fuzzer under AddressSanitizer to confirm the [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack‐buffer‐overflow is resolved.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Run the full test suite to ensure no regressions.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis single change addresses the buffer‐overflow by steering the input formatter to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe correct pathway and preserving all existing behavior of named‐color devicelink [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcreation.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1061[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1062[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This function creates a named color profile dumping all the contents of [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform to a single profile[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1063[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m In this way, LittleCMS may be used to [0m[32m"group"[0m[39m several named color databases[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto a single profile.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1064[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m It has, however, several minor limitations. PCS is always Lab, which is not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery critic since this[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1065[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m is the normal PCS for named color profiles.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1066[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m1067:c[0m[39mmsHPROFILE [0m[1;35mCreateNamedColorDevicelink[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsHTRANSFORM xform[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1068[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1069[0m[39m:    _cmsTRANSFORM* v = [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m xform;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1070[0m[39m:    cmsHPROFILE hICC = NULL;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1071[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number i, nColors;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1072[0m[39m:    cmsNAMEDCOLORLIST *nc2 = NULL, *Original = NULL;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1073[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1074[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Create an empty placeholder[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1075[0m[39m:    hICC = [0m[1;35mcmsCreateProfilePlaceholder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ContextID[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1076[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return NULL;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1077[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1078[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Critical information[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1079[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsSetDeviceClass[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC, cmsSigNamedColorClass[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1080[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsSetColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC, v ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1081[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsSetPCS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC, cmsSigLabData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1082[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1083[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Tag profile with information[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1084[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mSetTextTags[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC, L"Named color devicelink"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1085[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1086[0m[39m:    Original = [0m[1;35mcmsGetNamedColorList[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1087[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOriginal == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1088[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1090[0m[39m:    nc2     = [0m[1;35mcmsDupNamedColorList[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOriginal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1091[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnc2 == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1092[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1094[0m[39m:    nc2 ->ColorantCount = [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineOutputChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->Lut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1095[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1105[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1106[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mcmsWriteTag[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC, cmsSigNamedColor2Tag, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m nc2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1107[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsFreeNamedColorList[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnc2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1110[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m1111:E[0m[39mrror:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1112[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mcmsCloseProfile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhICC[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1114[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1115[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1116[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1117[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This structure holds information about which MPU can be stored on a profile[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbased on the version[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m floating point. Floating point is supported only in a subset, those formats [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This macro return words stored as big endian[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mCHANGE_ENDIAN[0m[1;39m([0m[39mw[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mw[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m<<[0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mw[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m>>[0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mREVERSE_FLAVOR_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m-[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m908[0m[39m:                       [0m[1;35mParalellizeIfSuitable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m909[0m[39m:                       return p;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m910[0m[39m:                   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m911[0m[39m:               [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m912[0m[39m:           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m913[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m914[0m[39m:           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Not suitable for the transform plug-in, let's check  the pipeline[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplug-in[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m915[0m[39m:           [0m[1;35m_cmsOptimizePipeline[0m[1;39m([0m[39mContextID, &p->Lut, Intent, InputFormat, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOutputFormat, dwFlags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m916[0m[39m:       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m917[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m918[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check whatever this is a true floating point transform[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m919[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsFormatterIsFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35m_cmsFormatterIsFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m920[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root‐cause analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow occurs because `cmsDoTransform` for named‐color index uses the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgeneric [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit “chunky” unpacker [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to read the input index, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreading one byte at a time from the address of a [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit stack variable `i`. Under [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain bit‐flag combinations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtra, Premul, SwapFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, it will do a byte access [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpast the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m‐byte integer’s last byte, corrupting the next stack slot.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The earlier patch only adjusted the `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` flags in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CreateNamedColorDevicelink` but did not prevent `UnrollChunkyBytes` from being [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mselected as the input formatter.  Hence the same code path is still used, and the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow persists.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix strategy overview[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce a dedicated input‐formatter for `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m-bit pipeline path that safely and directly reads a [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit index [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno “chunky” [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Register this new formatter so that when `InputFormat` is [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX`, the transform system picks `UnrollNamedColorIndex16` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mour[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew function[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of `UnrollChunkyBytes`.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` calls `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` with [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrect input flags [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m so the packer knows to expect exactly [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes × [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. In src/cmspack.c:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Define a new unpacker function for named‐color indices:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        static[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt8Number* [0m[1;35mUnrollNamedColorIndex16[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCMSREGISTER _cmsTRANSFORM* info,[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                                CMSREGISTER cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                                CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* accum,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                                CMSREGISTER cmsUInt32Number Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Read a [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit unsigned index from [0m[32m'accum'[0m[39m without overrun[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            cmsUInt32Number index;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m memcpy honors host endianness or use _cmsAdjustEndianess if [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnecessary[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&index, accum, sizeof index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Truncate or clamp to [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit pipeline domain[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mindex & [0m[1;36m0xFFFF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Advance by exactly [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return accum + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mindex[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. In the formatter‐registration table for [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit input formatters [0m[1;39m([0m[39musually [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnear the top of cmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Insert an entry before the generic `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` [0m[35m/[0m[39m fallback [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat maps the type to `UnrollNamedColorIndex16`.  For example:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m In cmsFormatters16[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m or equivalent:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,    [0m[1;35mTYPE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39m #bits for TYPE [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m* mask *[0m[35m/[0m[39m,  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollNamedColorIndex16 [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m,[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing entries follow[0m[33m...[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Ensure the mask matches only the type bits, not bytes or channels bits.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Rebuild `[0m[1;35m_cmsGetFormatter[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, cmsFormatterInput, CMS_PACK_FLAGS_16BITS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mso that it returns `UnrollNamedColorIndex16` when `info->InputFormat` has [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` in its type field.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. In src/cmsvirt.c [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. As in the last patch, set the input format to a single [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte channel:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Leave the transform loop unchanged:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```c[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Now, when `cmsDoTransform` is invoked, the internal formatter lookup will [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpick `UnrollNamedColorIndex16`, safely reading the [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit index from the address of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`i` without any one-byte overrun.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of existing logic[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We only add a new specialized formatter and register it under the existing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` type.  Other uses of `UnrollChunkyBytes` for genuine [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimage data remain unchanged.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not alter fuzz harness code, test code, or remove any functionality.  We[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimply introduce a correct input routine for named‐color transforms.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Why this approach is optimal[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Directly addresses the misuse of `UnrollChunkyBytes` for named‐color inputs.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Localizes the change to the packer/formatter subsystem without broadening [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception handling or reshaping stack layouts.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserves the existing `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call and the high-level logic [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar to other special‐case formatters already in the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvs. float routines[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, this solution uses the same registration mechanism and avoids [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munexpected side effects in unrelated code paths.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential side effects and mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the new formatter’s `mask` logic in the table does not overlap with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother types [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit, float[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  Tests for other pipelines should confirm no [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregressions.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm host endianness assumptions; if little/big‐endian conversion is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneeded, apply `_cmsAdjustEndianess32` before writing into `index`.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a small unit test for named‐color devicelink creation to verify no crashes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand correct palette output.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
